metadata.name: The First Shit
metadata.description:
The first shit.

The shittiest collection on the Ethereum blockchain.  
Literally nothing special. I ain't promising shit. Wait..no that's exactly what I'm promising. You're literally buying images of (drawn) shit, nothing more.  
Maybe in the future, shit holders can get some shit for holding their shit. Let's call it Constipate-To-Earn. If that shit ever happens anyway. SHIT!
